   <mods:abstract>Writes to acknowledge receipt of letters, and to suggest that Jay use a
            black ribbon to cure his sore throat. The camphor in the ribbon is said to have a
            medicinal effect. Hopes that John Jay will not consider him too
            credulous.</mods:abstract>
